name: AZAR (or decisions?)
description:
From the series: "Reflexiones del Tiempo" which has 25 images and a writing.

On this occasion, the invitation is to reflect on chance, on uncertainty: do we have %100 of control of our life? What do you think?chance or decisions?maybe both? which side will the coin fall on? Is it going to fall?

If you like to talk about this topics then we can continue to investigate this together by twitter, big hug.
